OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FAdam Fowler reports on the rising tide
OL,7,Fof abuse faced by GP surgery staff in
OL,8,FSouth Yorkshire
OL,10,FStaff working in GP surgeries have
OL,11,Fspoken out about the racial abuse and
OL,12,Fphysical threats they face after
OL,13,Fstatistics revealed 95% of workers in
OL,14,FSouth Yorkshire had been targeted by
OL,15,Fpatients.
OL,17,FPrimary Care Sheffield (PCS), which
OL,18,Fsupports 75 GP practices in the city,
OL,19,Fhas launched a campaign to encourage
OL,20,Fkindness following a rise in incidents.
