OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FYvonne, a receptionist at one surgery
OL,7,Fin Sheffield, said: "I've had
OL,8,Fcolleagues that have been racially
OL,9,Fabused and things like that.
OL,11,F"But now they're getting threats -
OL,12,F'I'm going to do your car', 'I'm going
OL,13,Fto stab you', 'I'm going to throw this
OL,14,Fat you'.
OL,16,F"There have been surgeries where
OL,17,Fcomputers have been thrown in
OL,18,Freception, so it's definitely getting
OL,19,Fmore on the physical side."
