OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FFigures from PCS show that, in South
OL,7,FYorkshire, 95% of staff in GP
OL,8,Fsurgeries have experienced verbal
OL,9,Fabuse. More than half have faced
OL,10,Fintimidation and over a third have
OL,11,Fbeen threatened with physical violence.
OL,13,FOne in six have been attacked.
OL,15,FThe campaign, called Don't Leave A
OL,16,FGap, highlights the impact when staff
OL,17,Fhave to take time off work or resign
OL,18,Faltogether due to stress.
