OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,FLiz, another receptionist in
OL,7,FSheffield, recently returned to work
OL,8,Fafter seven weeks off.
OL,10,F"You just put the phone down and
OL,11,F(think) I can't do this job any more.
OL,12,FThat's how it gets you," she said.
OL,14,F"It's just constant - the demands are
OL,15,Fthat high. You try to do your best and
OL,16,Fit's, it's not enough."
OL,18,FPCS medical director Dr Lucy Cormack
OL,19,Fsaid patients would experience the
OL,20,Fconsequences when staff struggle to
OL,21,Fcope.
