OL,3,C'I'm going to stab you': Rise in abuse
OL,4,Cof GP staff
OL,6,F"If you don't have staff in surgeries,
OL,7,Fthen people can't get access," she
OL,8,Fsaid "The phones don't get answered
OL,9,Fquickly enough, we reduce appointment
OL,10,Ftimes. It causes a huge knock on
OL,11,Fimpact to the rest of the service."
OL,13,FDoncaster GP Prof Vijay Kumar is a
OL,14,Fmember of the Royal College of GPs,
OL,15,Fwhich discussed rising abuse at a
OL,16,Frecent meeting.
OL,18,FHe said record waiting lists
OL,19,Fcontributed to patient frustration.
