OL,6,F"Never in the history of NHS in my
OL,7,Fcareer have I come across this number
OL,8,Fwaiting," he said. "The frustration
OL,9,Fseems to be taken out against primary
OL,10,Fcare staff. Where else can patients
OL,11,Fturn?"
OL,13,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,14,Fsaid the problem was "unacceptable".
OL,16,FA spokesperson said: "GPs have our
OL,17,Ffull support in refusing to treat or
OL,18,Freporting to police abusive patients.
